[ 1337.530277] BUG: KASAN: stack-out-of-bounds in bnxt_qplib_rcfw_send_message+0x40a/0x850 [bnxt_re]
[ 1337.530413] Read of size 16 at addr ffff888725477a48 by task rmmod/2785

